em zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527065\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527065\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 04, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ebm1665702598309.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ebm1665702598309.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ebm1665702598309.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ebm1665702598309\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ebm1665702598309__lookup_227250\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Count the number of occurrences that match the current profile.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ebm1665702598309__topic_d74180e1_d74181e1_d74182e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ebm1665702598309__p_d74183e1_d74184e1_d74185e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lookup</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ebm1665702598309__topic_d48882e1_d48883e1_d48884e1_d48885e1_d48886e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d734449e65\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6902e1_d6903e1_d6904e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6902e1_d6903e1_d6904e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6902e1_d6903e1_d6904e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6902e1_d6903e1_d6904e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&gt;=0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6902e1_d6903e1_d6904e1__entry__2\">\n Number of hits that match the profile.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6902e1_d6903e1_d6904e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6902e1_d6903e1_d6904e1__entry__2\">\n Record not found: end of file encountered.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6902e1_d6903e1_d6904e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-2</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6902e1_d6903e1_d6904e1__entry__2\">\n Occurrence not found: table is empty. (The table or file has no occurrences.)\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6902e1_d6903e1_d6904e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-3</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6902e1_d6903e1_d6904e1__entry__2\">\n Exceptional I/O error (hardware or software).\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6902e1_d6903e1_d6904e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-4</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6902e1_d6903e1_d6904e1__entry__2\">\n Open request for table or file failed. The table or file is not painted, or it does not exist.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6902e1_d6903e1_d6904e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-15</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6902e1_d6903e1_d6904e1__entry__2\">\n Uniface network error.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6902e1_d6903e1_d6904e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-16</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6902e1_d6903e1_d6904e1__entry__2\">\n Network error: unknown.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6905e1_d6906e1_d6907e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values commonly returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lookup</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6905e1_d6906e1_d6907e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6905e1_d6906e1_d6907e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6905e1_d6906e1_d6907e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6905e1_d6906e1_d6907e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-2</code> through <code class=\"ph codeph\">-12</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6905e1_d6906e1_d6907e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UIOSERR_*&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6905e1_d6906e1_d6907e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Errors during database I/O.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6905e1_d6906e1_d6907e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-16</code> through <code class=\"ph codeph\">-30</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6905e1_d6906e1_d6907e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UNETERR_*&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ebm1665702598309__table_d6905e1_d6906e1_d6907e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Errors during network I/O.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ebm1665702598309__topic_d48887e1_d48888e1_d48889e1_d48890e1_d48891e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d734449e269\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ebm1665702598309__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ebm1665702598309__topic_d48892e1_d48893e1_d48894e1_d48895e1_d48896e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d734449e278\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ebm1665702598309__p_d74198e1_d74199e1_d74200e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lookup</span> statement checks the database for an occurrence of the current entity with the primary key values of the current occurrence. If the complete primary key is not available, all field values are used. The number of hits that match this profile is returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>. No data is transported and the read trigger is not activated. If you want to find the total number of occurrences in the database of an entity, use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">clear</span> before you use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lookup</span>.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"ebm1665702598309__note_w1684ab1b7b9b5_w1685ab1b7b9_w1686ab1b7_w1687ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> A <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/o</span> may be faster than a\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lookup</span> statement, and it also checks data in the component.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ebm1665702598309__section_hp4_42h_ybc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d734449e309\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lookup</span></h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example uses the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lookup</span> statement to\n            check if a record with the number entered by the user already exists. The example\n            assumes that INVOICE_NUMBER is a primary key.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ebm1665702598309__pre_dzz_42h_ybc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger loseFocus\n; field : INVOICE_NUMBER\n; if another record already has this number\n; prevent user from leaving field\n\nlookup\nif ($status &gt; 0)\n message \"No! This number has been used before!\"\n return (-1)\nelse\n message \"I/O error %%$status\"\nendif\nend; loseFocus</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fgk1665702598390.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$hits</a><p>Return the number of occurrences in the hitlist.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rig1719386303130.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>clear</a><p>Clear data from the component or entity.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vvq1665702552959.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>read</a><p>Set the access mode.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kld1665702599590.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>retrieve/o</a><p>Attempt to locate an occurrence of an entity using the current primary key value.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ubp1665702661359.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>selectdb</a><p>Calculate aggregate values for specified fields in the database.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527065\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527065\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "lookup Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 04, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Count the number of occurrences that match the current profile. lookup Return Values Table 1. Values returned in $status Value Meaning >=0 Number of hits that match the profile. -1 Record not found: end of file encountered. -2 Occurrence not found: table is empty. (The table or file has no occurrences.) -3 Exceptional I/O error (hardware or software). -4 Open request for table or file failed. The table or file is not painted, or it does not exist. -15 Uniface network error. -16 Network error: unknown. Table 2. Values commonly returned by $procerror following lookup Value Error constant Meaning -2 through -12 <UIOSERR_*> Errors during database I/O. -16 through -30 <UNETERR_*> Errors during network I/O. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The lookup statement checks the database for an occurrence of the current entity with the primary key values of the current occurrence. If the complete primary key is not available, all field values are used. The number of hits that match this profile is returned in $status . No data is transported and the read trigger is not activated. If you want to find the total number of occurrences in the database of an entity, use clear before you use lookup . Note: A retrieve/o may be faster than a lookup statement, and it also checks data in the component. Example: Using lookup The following example uses the lookup statement to check if a record with the number entered by the user already exists. The example assumes that INVOICE_NUMBER is a primary key. trigger loseFocus ; field : INVOICE_NUMBER ; if another record already has this number ; prevent user from leaving field lookup if ($status > 0) message \"No! This number has been used before!\" return (-1) else message \"I/O error %%$status\" endif end; loseFocus Copy Related Links $hits Return the number of occurrences in the hitlist. clear Clear data from the component or entity. read Set the access mode. retrieve/o Attempt to locate an occurrence of an entity using the current primary key value. selectdb Calculate aggregate values for specified fields in the database. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}